     </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 call-to-action">
      <div class=" tk-pragmatica-web-condensed">
         <span style="font-size: 1.2em;">Art, Chocolate &amp; Spices</span><br/>
         We grow and dry our own herbs and spices for:<br/><%= link_to 'E8 Chocolate', e8_chocolate_path %>, <%= link_to 'Dalston Tea Time', dalston_tea_time_path %> and <%= link_to 'Hot, Hot Hot Chocolate', hot_chocolate_path %>
       </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
